category: Python
requires: python39 python39-asttokens python39-executing python39-pure-eval
sdesc: "This is a library that extracts data from stack frames and tracebacks, particularly to display more useful tracebacks than the default. It powers the tracebacks in IPython and futurecoder."
ldesc: "This is a library that extracts data from stack frames and tracebacks, particularly to display more useful tracebacks than the default. It powers the tracebacks in IPython and futurecoder."
